subtests.name: Property offset-anchor value 'left bottom' computes to '0% 100%'
Property offset-anchor value 'center center' computes to '50% 50%'
Property offset-anchor value 'right center' computes to '100% 50%'
Property offset-anchor value 'center top' computes to '50% 0%'
Property offset-anchor value 'center bottom' computes to '50% 100%'
Property offset-anchor value 'calc(20% - 5em) center' computes to 'calc(20% - 200px) 50%'
Property offset-anchor value 'left -10px top -20%' computes to '-10px -20%'
Property offset-anchor value 'right 10% bottom 20em' computes to '90% calc(100% - 800px)'
Property offset-anchor value 'top 10px right -20%' computes to '120% 10px'
Property offset-anchor value 'left 10% bottom 20em' computes to '10% calc(100% - 800px)'
Property offset-anchor value 'calc(10px - 0.5em) calc(10px + 0.5em)' computes to '-10px 30px'
